name: Rare Satoshi Society
about:
The Rare Satoshi Society is a distinguished community of blockchain enthusiasts committed to the purest pursuit of satoshis. Join us in our quest to forge a new path with the most ancient of sats, and become a part of the premiere hangout for ordinal degens and sat hunters. 
At RSS, we're dedicated to building an ecosystem where individuals can connect, learn, and share resources that promote the growth and evolution of the satoshi. Your .sats membership pass is your exclusive access to stellar alpha, our future collaborations with big names in the Ordinals space, prime giveaways, whitelists and much more. We are building furiously! Anyone can join the Discord, but only pass holders will truly cherish the secrets of the satoshi!
how-to-buy: We are currently on OrdSwap and Ordinals Wallet. We are listed on Ordynals and Ordinals Directory. Coming soon - OrdKit.
value-proposiion: We are the one-stop shop for Ordinals. We are continually farming links, airdrops, new alpha and more!
